          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Who should use the Placenta Sakura product?",
            "content": "<p>This product is ideal for customers over 30 who are experiencing signs of aging such as wrinkles, sagging skin, dryness, and dullness. It is also suitable for those facing hormonal imbalances or disorders during stages like postpartum, pre-menopause, or menopause. Additionally, it is a good choice for individuals who often feel fatigued, stressed, physically heavy, or are looking to achieve a slimmer, more balanced body shape.</p>",
            "open_by_default": true
          }
        },
        "item_wGGX4D": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "I’m over 30, my skin looks dull and dry, and I have hormonal imbalances. Can I use the Sakura Placenta product?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, you can use the Sakura Placenta product. For best results, combine it with a balanced diet and a healthy lifestyle, including regular exercise, to improve your health both internally and externally.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "item_QUdkMG": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Will taking this product cause weight gain?",
            "content": "<p>Whether you gain weight largely depends on your individual metabolism and how your body absorbs nutrients. 82X products do not contain fat, so they do not cause weight gain.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "item_FwXRPR": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I take the Collagen line in the morning and the Placenta line in the afternoon?",
            "content": "<p>To ensure optimal effectiveness, it is recommended to finish one product (such as Collagen) before starting the Placenta line, rather than taking them alternately or splitting them between morning and afternoon. Using both in this way may lead to excess nutrient intake and may not ensure optimal product quality during storage</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "item_8mizyR": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What time of day is best to use this product for optimal results?",
            "content": "<p>Experts recommend using the product in the morning between 9-10 am after breakfast or in the evening one hour before bedtime.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        }
